  "description": "<p>Superlight and low-profile, the Vapor Helmet offers some welcomed airflow and a comfortable fit. The lightness and generous ventilation make it a great cragging lid, proving helmets aren't just for multi-pitch trad climbs and big alpine faces.</p><ul><li>Super-light ALUULA composite with a polycarbonate shell for added protection and reduced weight</li><li>Geometric, open-air design provides airflow</li><li>Moulded EPP foam sides provide ample venting with the same sleek look</li><li>Cord fit suspension system fits inside the helmet for storage in your pack or haul bag</li><li>Removable headlamp clips secure a light on pre-dawn starts or when rapping after dark</li></ul>",
